    JoinConditionHelper<JoinedQLBuilder>, JoinedQLBuilder, QLBuilder

     class JoinedQLBuilderImpl
extends DelegatingQLBuilder
implements JoinedQLBuilder
    Builder implementation for a Join. This doesn't need all the private Members of the root, so this acts as a delegate.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
